";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Melissa Hoppe";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2337:"<p>Brian is taking a trip across the ocean to speak at <a href="http://2014.norway.wordcamp.org/">WordCamp Norway</a> this year! <a href="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screenshot_on_1.22.2014_at_10.57.00_AM.png"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-8022" alt="Screenshot_on_1.22.2014_at_10.57.00_AM" src="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screenshot_on_1.22.2014_at_10.57.00_AM.png" width="315" height="204" /></a>WordCamp Norway is being held at the <a title="Radisson Blu Hotel Nydalen, Oslo" href="http://www.radissonblu.no/hotellnydalen-oslo" target="_blank">Radisson Blu Hotel Nydalen, Oslo</a>. The event will run from the 25th to the 26th of January. You can view the entire schedule of WordCamp Norway on their <a href="http://2014.norway.wordcamp.org/schedule/">website</a>.</p>\n<p>Brian is speaking at <strong>15:20 CET on Saturday, January 25th in Room 1</strong>. He will be teaching you all about <span style="text-decoration: underline">Building Web Apps with WordPress. </span></p>\n<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>\n<p><em>WordPress started out as a blogging platform, but throughout the past 10 years, it has become so much more. It doesn&#8217;t matter if you&#8217;re new to the WordPress world, or if you have years of experience under your belt; with WordPress, you can make the impossible, possible. Brian will go through how to build and secure applications at a rapid pace, along with tips on how to save time and money while doing so. You will also get the opportunity to see some awesome apps and examples of things you can do with WordPress while drawing outside of the lines.</em></p>\n<p><em>Brian will also be speaking about <a href="http://apppresser.com/">AppPresser</a> &#8212; The first plugin framework that allows you to create native apps for iOS and/or Android using WordPress. He will illustrate how using AppPresser to create apps is just as easy as creating and customizing a WordPress website.</em></p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t get the opportunity to speak with Brian during WordCamp hours, you can catch him at the after party which is being held at the venue itself in the Radisson hotel bar. As always, Brian is excited to reconnect with those of you he&#8217;s already met, and to connect for the first time with those of you he hasn&#8217;t!</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/01/22/brian-messenlehner-is-speaking-at-wordcamp-norway-2014/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"3";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"WDS at WordCamp Phoenix 2014";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/01/15/wds-at-wordcamp-phoenix-2014/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/01/15/wds-at-